| create each other,^(A)            | sage or the creatures that are    |
|                                   | the ones acting in this and the   |
| Difficult and easy complete each  | following lines, so it is left    |
| other,                            | ambiguous here as well            |
|                                   |                                   |
| Long{lasting} and short{brief}    |                                   |
| contrast^(B) each other,          |                                   |
