Chapter Twenty Eight

+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| 知 其 雄 守 其 雌                 | Know your maleness, but maintain  |
|                                   | your femaleness.                  |
| 為 天 下 谿                       |                                   |
|                                   | Serve as a stream to the          |
| 為 天 下 谿                       | world.                            |
|                                   |                                   |
| 常 德 不 離                       | Serving as a stream to the world, |
|                                   |                                   |
| 復 歸 於 嬰 兒                    | The ever-constant De will not     |
|                                   | depart,                           |
| 知 其 白 守 其 黑 •               |                                   |
|                                   | Returning you to the state of the |
| 為 天 下 式                       | newborn infant.                   |
|                                   |                                   |
| 為 天 下 式                       |                                   |
|                                   |                                   |
| 常 德 不 忒                       | Know your brightness, but         |
|                                   | maintain your darkness.           |
| 復 歸 於 無 極                    |                                   |
|                                   | Serve as an example to the world. |
| 知 其 榮 守 其 辱                 |                                   |
|                                   | Serving as an example to the      |
