|                                   | hoodlums do not meet their        |
|                                   |                                   |
|                                   |       natural death.              |
|                                   |                                   |
|                                   | I will thus become their elder    |
|                                   | teacher.                          |
+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| ♦Dao creates one.                 | Notes                             |
|                                   |                                   |
| ♦One creates two.                 | A : compare to #40, where         |
|                                   | creatures are created from being  |
