|       place to display them.^(D)  | knotted ropes used to be used for |
|                                   | record-keeping                    |
| ♦Ensure that the citizens return  |                                   |
| to knotting ropes and using       |                                   |
|                                   |                                   |
|       them^(E),                   | Cross-references                  |
|                                   |                                   |
|                                   | nobles (in general) : #32, #37,   |
