|                 | skilled         |                 |                 |
|                 |                 | create, life,   |                 |
|                 | ! (#2)          | produce         |                 |
|                 |                 |                 |                 |
|                 | sage            | one             |                 |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+
| Strong          | benefit,        |                 |                 |
